text: How's your week going so far?

Asking if the date still works for the person gives them the flexibility to say yes or no. This is a good thing.
let's see. what are you in the mood for?
This can go either way. Giving options first can show you're thoughtful. Leaving it open gives a higher chance that she will enjoy the spot and feel comfortable - if she has a ready answer.
